        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Crypto4"><a href="#Crypto4" class="headerlink" title="Crypto4"></a>Crypto4</h1><p>题目来源：XCTF 不仅仅是Morse</p><p><img src="/lunan0320.github.io/2021/01/09/crypto4/1.png"></p><p>​    首先看到题目是morse密码的格式，直接在线解密工具</p><p><img src="/lunan0320.github.io/2021/01/09/crypto4/2.png"></p><p>​    观察破解出来的后半部分，只有A和B两个组成，通过这个特征，容易想到培根密码的形式</p><p>AAAAABAABBBAABBAAAAAAAABAABABAAAAAAABBABAAABBAAABBAABAAAABABAABAAABBABAAABAAABAABABBAABBBABAAABABABBAAABBABAAABAABAABAAAABBABBAABBAABAABAAABAABAABAABABAABBABAAAABBABAABBA</p><p>​    在线培根密码对后半部分解密之后可以得到结果：</p><p><img src="/lunan0320.github.io/2021/01/09/crypto4/3.png"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
